<lb n="0452a13"/><head type="no">No. 180</head>
<lb n="0452a14"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0452002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0452002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452002"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>過去<note n="0452003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世〕－【三】</note><note n="0452003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔世〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452003"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>佛分衛經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0452a15"/>
<lb n="0452a16"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0452004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔西晉…三藏〕七字－【宋】</note><app n="0452004" word-count="7"><lem>西晉<note n="0452005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔月氏國〕－【元】【明】</note><app n="0452005"><lem>月氏國</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0452006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三藏＋（法師）【元】【明】</note><app n="0452006"><lem>三藏</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">三藏法師</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0452a17"/><div1 type="jing"><p>佛言。<note n="0452007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＋（去）【三】</note><note n="0452007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過＋（去）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452007"><lem>過</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">過去</rdg></app>世有佛入城分衛。與尊弟子諸菩
<lb n="0452a18"/>薩俱。弟子菩薩姿容相好皆悉端正。如本所
<lb n="0452a19"/>行各得其道。有一母人&CB00775;<note n="0452008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身＝娠【元】【明】</note><app n="0452008"><lem>身</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">娠</rdg></app>數月。見佛及
<lb n="0452a20"/>僧有所至<note n="0452009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奏＝湊【三】</note><note n="0452009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奏＝湊【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452009"><lem>奏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">湊</rdg></app>。心自計願我所懷子生。如此
<lb n="0452a21"/>使為沙門佛弟子。日月滿足即生安隱。兒亦
<lb n="0452a22"/>姝好與眾人異。母以恩愛無<note n="0452010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝厭【三】</note><note n="0452010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意＝厭【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452010"><lem>意</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">厭</rdg></app>令兒行作沙
<lb n="0452a23"/>門。中有覺意。即自念言。我前有願。若我生
<lb n="0452a24"/>子當使為道。兒今已生有異凡人。令我安隱
<lb n="0452a25"/>復無惡露。不可戀<note n="0452011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嫪＝&CB00387;【三】</note><note n="0452011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嫪＝&CB00387;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452011"><lem>嫪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00387;</rdg></app>恩愛之故違我本心。
<lb n="0452a26"/>子年七歲家復貧狹。即作二人飯具及三法
<lb n="0452a27"/>衣。手持澡瓶自將其子行詣佛所。稽首佛足
<lb n="0452a28"/>前白佛言。願哀我子使為沙門。令後得道身
<lb n="0452a29"/>形如佛。佛即聽之令作沙門。母以澡<note n="0452012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">灌＝罐【三】</note><note n="0452012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">灌＝罐【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452012"><lem>灌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">罐</rdg></app>前
<pb ed="T" id="T03.0180.0452b" n="0452b"/>
<lb n="0452b01"/><note n="0452013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洗＝酒【宋】</note><app n="0452013"><lem>洗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">酒</rdg></app>兒手。應時九龍從瓶口出。吐水灌兒手
<lb n="0452b02"/>中。澡訖殘水散兒頭上。水之潺<note n="0452014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">渧＝滴【三】</note><note n="0452014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">渧＝滴【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452014"><lem>渧</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">滴</rdg></app>於兒頭
<lb n="0452b03"/>上化成華蓋珠交絡帳。中有師子座上有坐
<lb n="0452b04"/>佛。佛笑口中五色光出。照十億佛剎。還遶佛
<lb n="0452b05"/>身從兒頂入。母以飯具前上佛并食其<note n="0452015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＋（子）【三】</note><note n="0452015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子＋（子）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452015"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">子子</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0452b06"/>便發無上平等道意。應時十億佛剎為六<note n="0452016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝返【三】</note><note n="0452016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">反＝返【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452016"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">返</rdg></app>
<lb n="0452b07"/>震動。眾剎諸佛皆自然現。佛以母飯飽。爾
<lb n="0452b08"/>所佛及諸比丘僧皆等飽足。其飯如故亦不
<lb n="0452b09"/>損減。母即歡喜。及無數天人皆得阿惟越致。
<lb n="0452b10"/>時兒髮墮成為沙門。即亦得立不退轉地。母
<lb n="0452b11"/>前白佛。今我所見有三可怪。我澡兒手九龍
<lb n="0452b12"/>吐水。此一可怪。澡已殘水散兒頭上化成寶
<lb n="0452b13"/>帳。及師子座上有坐佛。是二可怪。佛笑口
<lb n="0452b14"/>中光從兒頂入。是三可怪。願佛為我分別說
<lb n="0452b15"/>之。佛言。此兒<note n="0452017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00230;＝起【宋】，印【元】</note><note n="0452017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00230;＝起【宋】，＝印【元】</note><app n="0452017"><lem>&CB00230;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">起</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">印</rdg></app>後十四劫當得作佛。九龍
<lb n="0452b16"/>當浴師子座華蓋寶帳。佛笑光從兒頂入。皆
<lb n="0452b17"/>是其應。母聞佛言倍懷踊躍。後<note n="0452018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＋（得）【三】</note><note n="0452018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＋（得）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452018"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">當得</rdg></app>作母人
<lb n="0452b18"/>轉輪聖王。積七百世竟。其劫壽盡轉母人身。
<lb n="0452b19"/>當得阿惟越致。佛言。是時小兒我身是。我
<lb n="0452b20"/>今於世功德如是。諸天龍神一切人民聞佛
<lb n="0452b21"/>所說。皆得阿惟越致</p>
<lb n="0452b22"/><p>　無熱佛　性空佛　天王佛　金仁佛</p>
<lb n="0452b23"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0452019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0452019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452019"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>過去<note n="0452020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔世〕－【三】</note><note n="0452020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔世〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0452020"><lem>世</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>佛分衛經</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
